  <brief_title>Comparison of McGrath Series 5 and Airtraq Videolaryngoscope for Double-lumen Tube (DLT) Intubation</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomised Controlled Trial Comparing of McGrath Series 5 and Airtraq Videolaryngoscope for Double-lumen Tube Intubation in Patients With Low Airway Risk Index Score</official_title>
  <sponsors>
